overview: From the very beginning, there was a lot of snuff, brandy and filth. you can say that it was Full Fräs from the beginning ...  Here we get to get to know Birger who delivers one story crazier than the other and Olvert who has an ability to drive people crazy. Blyge Örjan has come a long way as a program host. He has both a children's program and his own romantic corner. We also get to follow life on the farm with Sven-August, Errolf and Kristian where most things revolve around a clear liquid. Also lots of sketches and song numbers.
title: Full fräs
